bcl:definition.bcl:text:
individual filer means an individual that is required under
securities legislation to make an NRD submission in accordance with this
Instrument;

NRD account means an account with a member of the Canadian
Payments Association from which fees may be paid with respect to NRD by electronic
pre-authorized debit;

NRD administrator means the Alberta Securities Commission
or a successor appointed by the securities regulatory authority to operate
NRD;
